snippet.textDisplay: I know they set up hundreds of lift station samplers throughout my county, they were very careful to keep the data from being too refined. a neighborhood, yes, a building no. one of my clients was in upper management for the program run at the state level. as he is a privacy advocate, he made sure to keep things from being too specific. very cool system.
